f2838ed5e59de4d73cde5c98354b87a8d3200190","Node name for S&R":"ShowText|pysssss","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.5.2"}},"widgets_values":["[Category] Cosplay / IP Character\n[Composition]\n  - Composition type: Slightly off-center right, utilizing the rule of thirds to balance the subject against the window light; the chair and legs form a diagonal leading line from bottom left to center.\n  - Subject position: Horizontal 55% center-right, vertical 40% middle.\n  - Aspect ratio: 3:4 (Portrait orientation)\n[Shot Scale]\n  - Shot type: Medium full shot (waist to head).\n  - Framing range: Captures the character from the mid-thighs up to the top of the hat, including the chair, lamp, and book.\n  - Body parts visible: Head, shoulders, torso, thighs, knees, and feet (clipped by frame).\n  - Visual features: The figure is slightly rotated facing left, with limbs arranged naturally for reading posture.\n[Visual Parameters]\n  - Perspective type: Standard (slight wide-angle to capture full body proportions).\n  - Perspective effect: Natural human vision, slight exaggeration of the legs due to proximity.\n  - Depth of field: Shallow, background blurred to emphasize the character and book.\n[Scene Description]\n  - Geography/terrain: Interior of a cozy library or study room.\n  - Weather/lighting: Mixed lighting; strong natural sunlight streaming from the left window, creating high contrast with the warm artificial glow from the desk lamp on the right.\n  - Color tonality: High-key whites (dress, hair) contrasted with deep shadows and warm amber tones from the lamp and sunlight.\n  - Spatial layering: Foreground: Character's legs and chair; Midground: Character torso and book; Background: Bookshelves and window sill.\n  - Style genre: Anime/illustration style cosplay photography.\n[Atmosphere/Mood] Quiet, studious, elegant, cozy.\n[Details/Texture] The fabric of the dress shows soft folds and ruffles; the hat has a matte texture with a satin ribbon; the book cover appears leather-like and embossed; skin tones are smooth and idealized; the wooden floor has a polished sheen.\n**Step-by-step reasoning:**\n1.  **Analyze Image Content**: The image depicts an anime-style character (likely a cosplay) sitting on a chair in a library setting, reading a book. The character has long silver hair, wears a white dress with lace details, and a bonnet-style hat. A window is on the left, and a desk lamp is on the right.\n2.  **Choose Category**: Based on the visual style (anime aesthetics) and subject (a person in costume), \"Cosplay\" or \"IP Character\" is the most appropriate category.\n3.  **Analyze Composition**: The subject is positioned slightly to the right of center, adhering to the rule of thirds. There is a diagonal line formed by the legs and chair. The composition is balanced with bright light from the left.\n4.  **Infer Perspective & Depth**: The perspective is standard/slight wide-angle to capture the full figure. The depth of field is shallow, blurring the bookshelves in the background to focus attention on the character.\n5.  **Generate Description**: Following the category fields, I will describe the lighting (mix of natural and artificial), textures (fabric, skin), and spatial arrangement (library setting).\n**Final Output Generation:** (Proceeding to English output as requested)."]},{"id":113,"type":"ShowText|pysssss","pos":[-1270,2110],"size":[390,520],"flags":{},"order":21,"mode":4,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"文本","name":"text","type":"STRING","link":277}],"outputs":[{"label":"字符串","localized_name":"字符串","name":"STRING","shape":6,"type":"STRING","links":null}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-custom-scripts","ver":"f2838ed5e59de4d73cde5c98354b87a8d3200190","Node name for S&R":"ShowText|pysssss","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.5.2"}},"widgets_values":[]},{"id":200,"type":"ShowText|pysssss","pos":[-1550,1270],"size":[530,540],"f